This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) because it proposes a novel optimization method for training deep neural networks. It is also likely to belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) because the proposed method is applied to convolutional neural networks for image classification tasks. Additionally, it may belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it deals with the optimization of neural networks. Finally, it may also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it involves natural language processing in the form of the paper's title and abstract.
